Automating Tweets with Selenium
This project shows you how to automate tweets using the Python Selenium library.

Prerequisites
Before you begin, you need to have the following:

Python 3 installed on your machine
Selenium library installed in Python
Chrome browser installed on your machine


Installation
Install the Selenium library using pip:
pip install selenium

Download the Chrome driver for your version of Chrome and place it in the project directory. You can download the Chrome driver from the following link: https://sites.google.com/a/chromium.org/chromedriver/downloads

Open Automating twitter, selenium bots.py and replace the email and password variables with your Twitter login credentials.

Replace the messages variable with the text you want to tweet.